<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; }
    .code { font-family: monospace; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 5px; padding: 10px; background: #eee; display: inline-block; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
    
    <p>Please verify your email address to complete your registration with the SDS Test System.</p>
    
    <p>Click the button below to verify your email:</p>
    
    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
    
    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    
    <p>{{verificationUrl}}</p>
    
    <p>This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>© 2026 Ministry of Labour and Social Security - Kingdom of Eswatini</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
